       What's this you wonder? Today, in beautiful Malaga, Spain, we have
       presented the latest innovation in our proven range of ground-based
       recharging systems: SRS dedicated to electric buses. The premiere,
       as part of the #PALOMA pilot project currently underway, sees a
       prototype of SRS for e-buses operating at a bus stop in front of
       the University of Malaga‚Äôs School of Industrial Engineering. It is
       equipped with a 200kW charger and is associated with 12m Linkker
       e-bus which is running on Bus Line 1, operated by EMT, the local
       transport operator.
